The Fungal kernel
=================

This is the home of the Fungal kernel project which implements 
a Plain Old Java Object (POJO) kernel environment.

Highlights of features:
-----------------------
* 100% Pure Java 6 implementation
* Bean definition language
* Lifecycle of beans
* Parallel deployment
* Dependency management
* Classloader architecture
* Deployer framework
* Hot deployment
* Communication protocol
* Core services

Homepage:
---------
http://fungal.github.com

Project:
--------
http://github.com/fungal
